Use bun building & testing this project! Please ensure that the project builds successfully and that all tests pass. Before building the project or running tests, be sure to in copy environment example file as follows:

```bash
cp app/.env.example app/.env
```

Before finishing, make sure that the project passes all linting with:

```bash
bun run lint
```

Tests should be run using:

```bash
bun run test
```
